      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Advanced: Scaredy-Cat",
        "Client": "Fearful Felyne",
        "Description": "It was so scary, Hunter! I was trying\r\nto get home when I got caught in\r\nthis creepy mist. It was so thick,\r\nI could barely see my whiskers!\r\nI heard a rustling noise and when\r\nI spun around, I saw it! A two-horned\r\ndemon! Please! Don\u0027t let it get me!",
